---
title: Double Peppered Beef Rump with Garlicky Roast Veggie Toss & Aioli
description: A crispy stack of colourful roasted veggies creates the base for a steak dish of joyous proportions. Tender slices of beef rump are adorned in herby seasoning and topped by aioli to take things up a notch. Now, if that doesn't sound like heaven on earth, we don't know what does!

